Veterinarians will insert the implant during surgery to reconstruct Parys' nose tomorrow.

He will then be sent home to recover with his new owner, Magdalena Smosarska, in Bialystok, and his new nose.

It is hoped the implant will not only restore his sense of smell, but help reconstruct the shape of his nose which was left disfigured by the accident.

